org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment

Class AssignmentMap<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.AssignmentAbstract<V,T>
      • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.AssignmentMap<V,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - Variable
    T - Value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assignment<V,T>

    public class AssignmentMap<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>
extends AssignmentAbstract<V,T>
    An assignment using a HashMap to store values of all the variables of the model. This class is slower to store and retrieve a value than AssignmentArray, but faster in retrieving a collection of assigned variables and values (methods Assignment.assignedVariables() and Assignment.assignedValues()).
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
